{"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"notebook":"AWS","section":"AWS Serverless","page":{"id":"0-2f9b875b16eca54aaf8e8ece4bcbb6ad!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2059","self":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/pages/0-2f9b875b16eca54aaf8e8ece4bcbb6ad!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2059","createdTime":"2017-12-31T06:39:35.659Z","title":"AWS SAM local 소개","createdByAppId":"","links":{"oneNoteEmbedUrl":{"href":"https://onedrive.live.com/redir.aspx?cid=bc575ab8e2ab9833&page=edit&resid=BC575AB8E2AB9833!2000&parId=BC575AB8E2AB9833!109&wd=target%28AWS%20Serverless.one%7C310eb790-101c-5d47-8187-ebe85d1c5958%2FAWS%20SAM%20local%20%EC%86%8C%EA%B0%9C%7C89c38307-a282-a046-9fb3-29f9a1fb4f62%2F%29"},"oneNoteClientUrl":{"href":"onenote:https://d.docs.live.net/bc575ab8e2ab9833/Documents/AWS/AWS%20Serverless.one#AWS%20SAM%20local%20%EC%86%8C%EA%B0%9C&section-id=310eb790-101c-5d47-8187-ebe85d1c5958&page-id=89c38307-a282-a046-9fb3-29f9a1fb4f62&end"},"oneNoteWebUrl":{"href":"https://onedrive.live.com/redir.aspx?cid=bc575ab8e2ab9833&page=edit&resid=BC575AB8E2AB9833!2000&parId=BC575AB8E2AB9833!109&wd=target%28AWS%20Serverless.one%7C310eb790-101c-5d47-8187-ebe85d1c5958%2FAWS%20SAM%20local%20%EC%86%8C%EA%B0%9C%7C89c38307-a282-a046-9fb3-29f9a1fb4f62%2F%29"}},"contentUrl":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/pages/0-2f9b875b16eca54aaf8e8ece4bcbb6ad!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2059/content","lastModifiedTime":"2018-10-31T02:39:39Z","parentSection@odata.context":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/$metadata#me/notes/sections('0-BC575AB8E2AB9833%212059')/pages('0-2f9b875b16eca54aaf8e8ece4bcbb6ad%211-BC575AB8E2AB9833%212059')/parentSection(id,name,self)/$entity","parentSection":{"id":"0-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2059","name":"AWS Serverless","self":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/sections/0-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2059"},"content":"       Serverless Application Model(SAM) 블로그         2017-08-14     https://aws.amazon.com/ko/blogs/korea/new-aws-sam-local-beta-build-and-test-serverless-applications-locally/     2018-10-31     https://aws.amazon.com/ko/blogs/korea/aws-serverless-application-model-sam-command-line-interface-build-test-and-debug-serverless-apps-locally/            GitHub SAM    https://github.com/awslabs/serverless-application-model        SAM 의 장점    SAM Local은 SAM의 아래와 같은 장점을 로컬 시스템으로 가져와서 사용 가능합니다.         sam local 및 Docker를 사용하여 AWS Lambda함수를 로컬에서 개발하고 테스트 가능     Amazon Simple Storage Service (S3), Amazon DynamoDB, Amazon Kinesis, Amazon Simple Notification Service (SNS) 등과 같은이벤트 소스에서 함수 호출을 시뮬레이션 가능     SAM 템플릿에서 로컬 Amazon API Gateway를 시작하고, 이를 시뮬레이션 가능     이를 통해 SAM 템플릿을 신속하게 검증하고 해당 유효성 검사를 linters 또는 IDE와 통합 가능     람다 함수에 대한 대화 형 디버깅 지원을 제공            SAM 의 단점(주관적)         CloudFormation과 artifact에 대한 지식이 얕은 사람들은 진입장벽이 조금 있을 것 같다     Docker 를 로컬에 설치해야 한다     배포 과정이 sam package 옵션... & sam deploy 옵션… 이렇게 두 번의 step을 거치는데, serverless framework에서는 sls deploy 간단한 문장 한 줄이면 해결 되는 것에 비해 뒤에 따라붙는 옵션 커맨드도 조금 알아야 하고 조금 불편하다           ","html":"\n\t\t<div style=\"position:absolute;left:46px;top:120px;width:577px\">\n\t\t\t<h2 lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">Serverless Application Model(SAM) <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xBE14;&#xB85C;&#xADF8;</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold\">2017-08-14</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/ko/blogs/korea/new-aws-sam-local-beta-build-and-test-serverless-applications-locally/\">https://aws.amazon.com/ko/blogs/korea/new-aws-sam-local-beta-build-and-test-serverless-applications-locally/</a></p>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold\">2018-10-31</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/ko/blogs/korea/aws-serverless-application-model-sam-command-line-interface-build-test-and-debug-serverless-apps-locally/\">https://aws.amazon.com/ko/blogs/korea/aws-serverless-application-model-sam-command-line-interface-build-test-and-debug-serverless-apps-locally/</a></p>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<h2 lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">GitHub SAM</h2>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><a href=\"https://github.com/awslabs/serverless-application-model\">https://github.com/awslabs/serverless-application-model</a></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<h2 lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">SAM <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC758;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC7A5;&#xC810;</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><a href=\"https://github.com/awslabs/aws-sam-local\" lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt\">SAM Local</a><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">&#xC740; SAM&#xC758; &#xC544;&#xB798;&#xC640; &#xAC19;&#xC740; &#xC7A5;&#xC810;&#xC744; &#xB85C;&#xCEEC; &#xC2DC;&#xC2A4;&#xD15C;&#xC73C;&#xB85C; &#xAC00;&#xC838;&#xC640;&#xC11C; &#xC0AC;&#xC6A9; &#xAC00;&#xB2A5;&#xD569;&#xB2C8;&#xB2E4;.</span></p>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#b12704;background-color:#f7f7f7\">sam local</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">&#xA0;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">&#xBC0F; Docker&#xB97C; &#xC0AC;&#xC6A9;&#xD558;&#xC5EC;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">&#xA0;</span><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/lambda/\" lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt\">AWS Lambda</a><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">&#xD568;&#xC218;&#xB97C; &#xB85C;&#xCEEC;&#xC5D0;&#xC11C; &#xAC1C;&#xBC1C;&#xD558;&#xACE0; &#xD14C;&#xC2A4;&#xD2B8; &#xAC00;&#xB2A5;</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span lang=\"en-US\"><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/s3/\" lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt\">Amazon Simple Storage Service (S3)</a><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">&#xA0;</span><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/dynamodb/\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt\">Amazon DynamoDB</a><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">&#xA0;</span><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/kinesis/\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt\">Amazon Kinesis</a><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">&#xA0;</span><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/sns/\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt\">Amazon Simple Notification Service (SNS)&#xA0;</a><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">&#xB4F1;&#xACFC; &#xAC19;&#xC740;&#xC774;&#xBCA4;&#xD2B8; &#xC18C;&#xC2A4;&#xC5D0;&#xC11C; &#xD568;&#xC218; &#xD638;&#xCD9C;&#xC744; &#xC2DC;&#xBBAC;&#xB808;&#xC774;&#xC158; &#xAC00;&#xB2A5;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">SAM &#xD15C;&#xD50C;&#xB9BF;&#xC5D0;&#xC11C; &#xB85C;&#xCEEC;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">&#xA0;</span><a href=\"http://aws.amazon.com/apigateway\" lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt\">Amazon API Gateway</a><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">&#xB97C; &#xC2DC;&#xC791;&#xD558;&#xACE0;, &#xC774;&#xB97C; &#xC2DC;&#xBBAC;&#xB808;&#xC774;&#xC158; &#xAC00;&#xB2A5;</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">&#xC774;&#xB97C; &#xD1B5;&#xD574; SAM &#xD15C;&#xD50C;&#xB9BF;&#xC744; &#xC2E0;&#xC18D;&#xD558;&#xAC8C; &#xAC80;&#xC99D;&#xD558;&#xACE0; &#xD574;&#xB2F9; &#xC720;&#xD6A8;&#xC131; &#xAC80;&#xC0AC;&#xB97C; linters &#xB610;&#xB294; IDE&#xC640; &#xD1B5;&#xD569; &#xAC00;&#xB2A5;</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">&#xB78C;&#xB2E4; &#xD568;&#xC218;&#xC5D0; &#xB300;&#xD55C; &#xB300;&#xD654; &#xD615; &#xB514;&#xBC84;&#xAE45; &#xC9C0;&#xC6D0;&#xC744; &#xC81C;&#xACF5;</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<h2 lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">SAM <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC758;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB2E8;&#xC810;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">(</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC8FC;&#xAD00;&#xC801;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">)</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span lang=\"en-US\">CloudFormation<span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xACFC;</span> artifact<span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC5D0;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xB300;&#xD55C;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC9C0;&#xC2DD;&#xC774;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC595;&#xC740;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC0AC;&#xB78C;&#xB4E4;&#xC740;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC9C4;&#xC785;&#xC7A5;&#xBCBD;&#xC774;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC870;&#xAE08;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC788;&#xC744;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xAC83;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xAC19;&#xB2E4;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold\">Docker</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xB97C;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xB85C;&#xCEEC;&#xC5D0;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC124;&#xCE58;&#xD574;&#xC57C;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xD55C;&#xB2E4;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>&#xBC30;&#xD3EC;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xACFC;&#xC815;&#xC774;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"color:#e84c22;background-color:silver\">sam package </span><span style=\"color:#e84c22;background-color:silver\">&#xC635;&#xC158;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"color:#e84c22;background-color:silver\">...</span><span lang=\"en-US\"> &amp; </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"color:#e84c22;background-color:silver\">sam deploy &#xC635;&#xC158;&#x2026;</span><span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xC774;&#xB807;&#xAC8C;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xB450;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xBC88;&#xC758;<span lang=\"en-US\"> step</span>&#xC744;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xAC70;&#xCE58;&#xB294;&#xB370;<span lang=\"en-US\">, </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-weight:bold\">serverless framework</span>&#xC5D0;&#xC11C;&#xB294;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"color:#e84c22;background-color:silver\">sls deploy</span><span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xAC04;&#xB2E8;&#xD55C;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xBB38;&#xC7A5;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xD55C;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xC904;&#xC774;&#xBA74;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xD574;&#xACB0;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xB418;&#xB294;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xAC83;&#xC5D0;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xBE44;&#xD574;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xB4A4;&#xC5D0;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xB530;&#xB77C;&#xBD99;&#xB294;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xC635;&#xC158;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xCEE4;&#xB9E8;&#xB4DC;&#xB3C4;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xC870;&#xAE08;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xC54C;&#xC544;&#xC57C;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xD558;&#xACE0;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xC870;&#xAE08;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xBD88;&#xD3B8;&#xD558;&#xB2E4;</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\n\n"}}}